1.title: Time Travel
1.plot: Strange things are happening in Om Nom's home. The floor is shaking, his candy is moving, and the room is filled with strange noises. Watch this sweet video and find out how Om Nom's time travel adventure began.

2.title: The Middle Ages
2.plot: Om Nom has traveled to The Middle Ages to find his ancestor. Does he have what it takes to pull the sword from the stone and join the Knights of the Candy Table? Find out in this sweet episode of Om Nom Stories.

3.title: The Renaissance
3.plot: Om Nom has set off on his latest time travel adventure. This time, he is visiting The Renaissance, an era filled with art, science, and, to Om Nom's delight, CANDY.

4.plot: Om Nom's time machine has delivered him to a tropical island. Find out if Om Nom has what it takes to help his ancestor find the sweetest treasure of all.

5.title: Ancient Egypt
5.plot: Most Pharaohs wanted their tombs to be filled with gold and silver. Fortunately, Om Nom's ancestor preferred something much tastier - CANDY. Find out if Om Nom is able to escape from the ancient tomb with his life, and candy, intact.

6.title: Ancient Greece
6.plot: Om Nom has arrived in Ancient Greece and is "helping" his ancestor Artist Om Nom to create a masterpiece. Find out if Om Nom's adventure as a sculptor results in a big success or just a big mess.

7.title: The Stone Age
7.plot: Om Nom has traveled back to the Stone Age and is looking for his ancestor. Watch Om Nom battle his way past carnivorous plants, giant insects, and baby dinosaurs on his mission to feed Prehistoric Om Nom with candy.

8.title: Disco Era
8.plot: Groovy. Om Nom has traveled back to the Disco Era in our latest Om Nom Stories episode. Watch the video now and find out if Om Nom and Disco Om Nom are as good at dancing as they are at eating candy.

9.title: Wild West
9.plot: Om Nom has traveled back to the Wild West in search of his ancestor Sheriff Om Nom. Watch Om Nom's wildest adventure yet and find out if his brush with the law results in a severe punishment or a sweet reward.

10.plot: Oh no - Om Nom is trapped in a time warp. Will he make it home safely? Watch this action-packed Om Nom Stories episode and see if Om Nom can navigate the winds of time and make it home sweet home.

4.plot: Om Nom is separated from his candy by a canyon in this surprising Om Nom Stories episode. Fortunately, with help from his new friend Blue, no gap is wide enough to keep Om Nom from his ultimate goal - CANDY.

5.title: City Park
5.plot: Om Nom battles howling winds and fierce rain in this gripping Om Nom Stories episode. Fortunately, with Toss by his side, no storm is too powerful and no building is too high to keep Om Nom from his candy.

6.title: Underground
6.plot: Om Nom gives Boo a taste of his own medicine in this Om Nom stories episode. Watch Om Nom as he battles past banana peels, cobwebs and dusty ventilation shafts on his quest for candy.

7.title: Fruit Market
7.plot: Om Nom has discovered another sweet location on his unexpected adventure -- the fruit market. Fortunately, with Snailbrow by his side, no pear is too prickly and no chasm too wide to stop Om Nom from reaching his candy.

8.title: Bakery
8.plot: Om Nom finds himself in the bakery. There he meets Ginger, who is dangerous on the first sight, but in the end appears to be really friendly and helps our hero get the candy.

imdb.plot outline: Om Nom Stories is a long-running kids comedy series featuring Om Nom - cute little monster whose curiosity often leads to funny situations. It was launched in 2012 by ZeptoLab - a UK company well know by its mobile game series Cut the Rope. Om Nom Stories cartoons were created with the intention to broaden Om Nom franchise and show fans a bigger story about their beloved character. Today Om Nom Stories have more than 10 BLN views worldwide and 80x3.5 episodes , with more content already in production. Its target audience are preschool children 0 to 6 y.o. The animated series can be found on major TV channels and VOD platforms, including Amazon (WW), ITV (UK), IVI, Karusel (RU), Movile (WW), ToonGoogles and many others. It also has more than 1M subscribers on its official YouTube channel. In addition to that, ZeptoLab has recently released its video content in China on Tencent Video, Youku and Iqiyi and already received over 1 BLN views in 2 months. Throughout the series, Om Nom discovers the time machine, travels around the world, creates his own video blog and even becomes a super hero. And although the character faces many challenges, he manages to stay kind and attentive to the needs of others, making many friends along the way. Om Nom appeals to the audience as kids recognize themselves in energetic green monster. And parents are happy that their child has such a perfect companion.
